Georgia Engel https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Georgia_Engel 0 Georgia Bright Engel (born July 28, 1948) is an American actress. She is best known for playing Georgette Franklin Baxter in the successful sitcom The Mary Tyler Moore Show from 1972 to 1977. During her career, Engel received five Primetime Emmy Award nominations.
